---
name: draft-mastodon
description: Draft a single post for Mastodon (500 char limit)
triggers:
  - draft a mastodon post
  - write something for mastodon
  - post to mastodon only
  - mastodon post only
---

Read the skill file at `.postlane/commands/draft-mastodon.md`, then draft one post for Mastodon. Output sets `platforms: ["mastodon"]` in `meta.json`.
